text: Žaklina Šojić is a Danish beauty pageant titleholder of Serb descent, who was crowned Miss Universe Danmark 2007 and represented Denmark at Miss Universe 2007 in Mexico City, Mexico. ==Early life== Žaklina is working as a model in Denmark. ==Pretty Danish 2007== Žaklina was crowned Miss Universe Denmark 2007.
